%A1-h%C3%A0nh-Ho%C3%A0ng-Sa-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-trung/poem-fi0AnZEbTlY085rk8ctF-w">Tây giang nguyệt - Dạ hành Hoàng Sa đạo trung - 西江月－夜行黃沙道中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/V%E1%BA%A1n-s%E1%BB%B1-quy-nh%C6%B0/poem-fpW7euMg85Nsgj5ASUIGQQ">Vạn sự quy như - 萬事歸如</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-XI/poem-TKTlzkslSejueTUbvK9wRw">Vô đề (XI) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-VNhahLxtqyIrLeDASL0s9Q">Thực Hiền</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%95/X%C3%A3-t%E1%BB%AB-h%E1%BB%AFu-ho%C3%A0i/poem-wE7pDTXkRFXCQ1V1NnP1LQ">Xã từ hữu hoài - 社祠有懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%95/author-qsdCXtvu8PM8SdkWmraV5A">Phạm Đình Hổ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
